THE ROLE
Expand all
This position will be focused on the implementation of Symantec security products within various customer environments.
Job responsibilities include assessing customer needs and expectations, designing solutions to meet those needs, and then implementing the design. In addition to these activities the consultant will participate in the sales process (proposal creation, presentations, sales calls, demos, etc.).
